Close Brace 5 Minute React: Express

--------
Commands
--------

start webserver: $ yarn start 
  
  (run from project dir)


---------------
Install & Setup
---------------

  Install Express-generator as a global module

    ** must be re-installed if switching node versions

    $ yarn global add express-generator

  Install the webserver

    cd to project parent dir

    $ express -v ejs -f projectdir

      (install express using EJS as a view engine in the projectdir folder even though theres already some stuff in there)

  Install modules from package.json

    switch to project dir

    $ yarn

